        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks WS for information about moss roses and the Le Compte family.</p> 
<p>Mentions WS’s recent papers on inheritance [<hi rend="italic">Brit. &amp; Foreign Med.-Chirurg. Rev.</hi> (1867)].</p> 
